{"tid":2416431,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"陳肇始：林鄭月娥班子率先接種疫苗能起示範作用","createTime":"2021-02-21T04:52:40.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-21T07:41:25.000Z","uid":212626,"like":8,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"18d35f4430df3cdf89a640d173c4d5823fc44c69","tid":2416431,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T04:52:40.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】行政長官以及全體司局長會在本周初率先接種疫苗，食物及衞生局局長陳肇始指，希望能在社會上起示範作用；又呼籲市民接種疫苗，讓社會盡早有群體免疫，為通關等提供有利條件。<br />\n<br />\n陳肇始：「對個人自己，當然接種一定比不接種好。如果問何時接種較好、是否要再觀望，我也呼籲大家早打一定比遲打好。對整個社會而言，愈多人接種，一定對社會的效益愈大。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=424776\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D424776&d=0FWZMlR46yIxX%2BJDTULvncpe%2FvQB%2B59L3xQItPRvby0%3D&h=35aa10d1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D424776&h=216515cb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=424776</a>"},{"pid":"506c6ff94ff43c7ca864f3fcded1623106bad713","tid":2416431,"uid":241239,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T04:53:35.000Z","msg":"咁你地咪打飽佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e4b73d8d5a705c2c685b7e7b38a1dbe6f93cb66","tid":2416431,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T04:55:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88c3e5a7495d0811872bcef1ea8f0575f30abb3d","tid":2416431,"uid":239336,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T04:56:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zt7f8Ot.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fzt7f8Ot.gif&h=f4bc58dc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1a8e3eeedafbfb31a85a13d791a2ce61a78aade6","tid":2416431,"uid":145923,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T04:57:04.000Z","ms